Class ExecutionResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.platform.testkit.ExecutionResults
  • @API(status=EXPERIMENTAL,
     since="1.4")
public class ExecutionResults
extends Object
    Represents the entirety of multiple test or container execution runs.
